data.description: Welcome to your future home in Deland's charming Sawyer's Landing community! This beautifully designed home, constructed in 2019, offers a spacious 2018 sq. ft. of living space with all of the modern comforts you'd expect. With 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, it's perfect for accommodating your family and guests. The open floor plan is great for entertaining and ideal for hosting gatherings and creating memories. The gourmet kitchen is a showstopper, complete with granite countertops, a double oven, 42-inch cabinets, and elegant crown molding, making it a culinary enthusiast's haven. Need a dedicated workspace or flex room? You'll love the versatile office that can adapt to your needs. Step outside and enjoy your mornings on the screened porch, perfect for sipping coffee as you take in the day. For those who love outdoor cooking, the pavered patio provides an excellent space for barbecuing and outdoor dining while maintaining privacy in your fenced-in backyard. You can rest easy with an ADT home security system for added peace of mind. Experience the benefits of a water filtration and purification system and gutters that enhance the property's functionality and comfort. Location is key, and this home doesn't disappoint. Situated near I-4, you'll have easy access to nearby downtown Deland and a variety of shopping opportunities. This home truly has it all. Don't wait, schedule a showing today!
